Vulois

Vulois cired out to his friends.

"All right! Everything in unpacked. Windrazor, Terradive and I will 
move everything to the new base. Child Eagle Eye and Afterburner will 
stay here and protect the stuff, because it will tkae many trips. 
Than finaly we will bring everybody in and we will put everything 
together again there. Alright? Good. Windazor and Terradive, get an 
armful of junk and follow me!"

Vulois picked up some computer boards and flew off towards his ship.
______________________________________________________________________
Brix/Fliq

Brix and Fliq loaded the boards into the shuttle, and than turned to 
Ramulus.

"Load your stuff in the back, and than we have a question to discuss. 
We only have enough room for Hull or Weapons. What will we take?"
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream was deeply mediatating when KitKat's scream pulled him out 
of it. He ran and ran and finaly came to the CR Chambers, where he 
saw Kitkat in it.

"No....Not again. They hurt you? Those diry Bastards! If only I 
hadn't been meditating, we would've been side by side on the front 
line, like you promised. I'm so sorry!(He turned to Drillbit.) Is the 
battle over? Did I miss it?"

(Some people may get mad at the way I'm portraying Starscream, since 
he's supposed to be ruthless and uncaring. Well this is the way I 
want to. He's changed and learned alot from wandering the Universe. I 
called him first so all I can say is Ha Ha!)
______________________________________________________________________
Gotron

"Oh! My name is Gotron. And I know yours. Anytime you need me, I will 
always be at your side Lord Zardus."
______________________________________________________________________
Zava

Zava pulls back beside Deemos.

"It seems most of the Predacons retreated, sir. Do we charge or pull 
back?"
